'''教會歷史博物館'''（{{lang-en|'''Church History Museum'''}}）是一座位於[[美國|美國]][[鹽湖城|鹽湖城]]的[[耶穌基督後期聖徒教會|耶穌基督後期聖徒教會]]博物館，對面是該教會[[神廟廣場|神廟廣場]]西門。在2008年11月之前被稱作'''教會歷史藝術博物館'''（'''Museum of Church History and Art'''）。<ref>{{cite news |title= Museum is now known as Church History Museum |date= November 15, 2008 |newspaper= [[LDS_Church_News|LDS Church News]] |url= http://www.ldschurchnews.com/articles/55920/Museum-is-now-known-as-Church-History-Museum.html |accessdate= 2013-08-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131114000631/http://www.ldschurchnews.com/articles/55920/Museum-is-now-known-as-Church-History-Museum.html |archive-date= 2013-11-14 |dead-url= yes }}</ref> 

==歷史==

該博物館的主要發起人是{{link-en|佛羅倫斯·S·雅各布森|Florence S. Jacobsen}}。1984年4月4日博物館正式開張。<ref>{{citation |contribution= New Church Museum Dedicated |title= News of the Church |journal= [[Ensign_(LDS_magazine)|Ensign]] |publisher= LDS Church |pages= 104–6 |url= http://www.lds.org/ensign/1984/05/news-of-the-church?lang=eng |first= Bob |last= Cazier |accessdate= 2013-08-20 |date= May 1984 |archive-date= 2013-10-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131021224221/http://www.lds.org/ensign/1984/05/news-of-the-church?lang=eng |dead-url= no }}</ref>

該博物館一星期全天開放，不收取費用，博物館商店在週日關門。

